15. Upgrade aplikasi pakai Helm
example change l'image tag de v1 à v2 et replica devient 3:

helm upgrade bro-release ./broapp \
  -n demo-helm \
  --set image.tag=v2 \
  --set replicaCount=3 \
  --set service.type=LoadBalancer

Check rollout:

kubectl rollout status deployment/bro-release-broapp -n demo-helm

Check pod:

kubectl get pods -n demo-helm -o wide

Check history Helm:

helm history bro-release -n demo-helm

