3. Install/Upgrade à AKS

pour lab, utilise le LoadBalancer:

helm upgrade --install bro-release . \
  -n demo-helm \
  --create-namespace \
  --set service.type=LoadBalancer \
  --atomic \
  --wait \
  --timeout 10m

--**--

les commands CLi important :

upgrade --install = si n'existe pas, install; si deja la ou put utliser diret "upgrade"
--atomic          = si crash, rollback otomatis
--wait            = attend resource ready
--timeout         = le limite temp attend

Check:

helm list -n demo-helm
kubectl get all -n demo-helm
kubectl get svc -n demo-helm


